\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.1}{\ignorespaces Structure of the input tensor for a single sliding window sample, consisting of 13 sensor channels over 70 consecutive time steps. Each slice in the depth direction represents one engine unit.}}{14}{figure.caption.7}%
